==Descendants==
Both daughters of Marshal Pi<U+0142>sudski returned to Poland in 1990, after the fall of communist system there. Daughter of Jadwiga Pi<U+0142>sudska, Joanna Jaraczewska returned to Poland in 1979. There, she married in a political prison a Polish [[Solidarity (Polish trade union)|"Solidarity"]] activist [[Janusz Onyszkiewicz]] in 1983. Both were very involved in the anticommunist struggle of Poles in the 1979<U+2013>89 decade.<ref>{{cite web|author=Editor: Julita Karkowska; Webmaster: Stanis<U+0142>aw Psyk |url=http://www.dziennik.com/www/dziennik/kult/archiwum/01-06-06/pp-03-03-02.html |title="Nowy Dziennik" weekly, on-line edition, in "Droga na szczyty" by T.Lachowicz |publisher=Dziennik.com |accessdate=24 July 2011}}</ref>

